            "content": "<p>Dr. Dennis Miller, a highly regarded Doctor of Chiropractic, graduated with honors from Palmer College of Chiro-practic, the top institution in the field, in 1976. He is an active member of the ICA and ICAC. Dr. Miller brings his ex-tensive expertise to our flagship products, providing professional solutions for sedentary users with AutoFull M6 series.</p>",
